President Donald Trump has announced his intention to nominate several individuals for judicial and marshal positions. A. Marvin Quattlebaum Jr. and Julius "Jay" N. Richardson have been nominated as Circuit Judges on the U.S. Court of Appeals for the Fourth Circuit. Richard J. Sullivan has been nominated as a Circuit Judge on the U.S. Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit. Roy K. Altman, Thomas P. Barber, Rodolfo "Rudy" Ruiz II, Rodney Smith, and T. Kent Wetherell II have been nominated as District Judges. Richard A. Hertling has been nominated as a Judge on the U.S. Court of Federal Claims. Kim Gaffney, Denny Wade King, Susan Lewellyn Pamerleau, Barrett W. Rich, Richard E. Taylor Jr., and Enoch "Nick" Willard have been nominated as United States Marshals.